{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01VGjtwYPZi69TajpU75WJcF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have all the numbers needed. Let me compile the memo and write it to A3.\n\nKey figures:\n- 386 vendors, $7,887,360 total LTM spend\n- Terminate: 344 vendors ($1,552,621, 19.7%) | Optimize: 25 ($6,189,417, 78.5%) | Consolidate: 17 ($145,322, 1.8%)\n- Top 10 = 63.9% of spend; Salesforce = 39.5% ($3,117,226)\n- Top 3 savings: Salesforce renegotiation ~$467K, Navan consolidation ~$73K, BDO+RSM right-sizing ~$92K = $632K total\n- Total identified savings: $1,552,621 (terminate) + $632K (optimize) + ~$29K (consolidate) = $2,213,621 (28.1%)"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":17265,"cache_read_input_tokens":17334,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":17265,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6052fd6a-0825-4d0d-b821-8264b77b2b81","uuid":"e6056670-e865-4cac-92ac-e3a09ee81770"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01VGjtwYPZi69TajpU75WJcF","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016w1MLtBL4yvpJxEpBXPFdN","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst XLSX = require('xlsx');\n\nconst filePath = 'C:/Users/rjega/vendor-spend-analysis/outputs/A - TEMPLATE - RWA - Vendor Spend Strategy (R Jegadeswari).xlsx';\n\nconst wb = XLSX.readFile(filePath);\nconst sheetName = 'CEOCFO Recommendations';\nconst ws = wb.Sheets[sheetName];\n\n// Confirm A1 and A2 before writing\nconsole.log('A1 type:', ws['A1'] ? ws['A1'].t : 'empty');\nconsole.log('A2 type:', ws['A2'] ? ws['A2'].t : 'empty');\nconsole.log('A3 exists:', !!ws['A3']);\nconsole.log('Sheet ref:', ws['!ref']);\n\"\n","description":"Confirm A1, A2, A3 state before writing"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":17265,"cache_read_input_tokens":17334,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":17265,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"6052fd6a-0825-4d0d-b821-8264b77b2b81","uuid":"efbbecdd-8e77-465d-b346-6721bdd7ff23"}
